INSERT INTO `contact_instances` VALUES (1,1,'I\'m just testing out the contact mailer.',0,'2011-10-05 18:27:16','2011-10-05 18:27:16'),(2,2,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-10-13 12:56:41','2011-10-13 12:56:41'),(3,2,'Hi. This is a test. ',1,'2011-10-13 13:03:26','2011-10-13 13:03:26'),(4,3,'Another test!',1,'2011-10-13 13:08:35','2011-10-13 13:08:35'),(5,3,'hello. me want to talk to you.',1,'2011-10-18 20:16:38','2011-10-18 20:16:38'),(6,3,'Me talk?',1,'2011-10-19 15:46:30','2011-10-19 15:46:30'),(7,4,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-11-10 20:06:57','2011-11-10 20:06:57'),(8,2,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-11-22 21:04:02','2011-11-22 21:04:02'),(9,5,'testing.',0,'2011-11-22 21:18:52','2011-11-22 21:18:52'),(10,2,'Test!',0,'2011-11-22 21:20:03','2011-11-22 21:20:03'),(11,6,'Hello My name is Michelle Zephier I am a single mother of five amazing children but am having a hard time with our utilities and propane bill.  I do work and have been able to get me and my children off of cash aid. We do still get foodstamps. If there is anything you can do to help us please let us know.  Or if you now of an agency that can help us please let us know.  Thank you for your time.\r\nMichelle A. Zephier\r\nPeach Springs, AZ  86434\r\n\r\nPhone:  (928) 769-1310\r\nFax:     (928) 769-1377\r\n',0,'2011-11-22 22:36:37','2011-11-22 22:36:37'),(12,7,'To whom it may concern my name is Shamunda I have sage 4 breast cancer this is not my first go around with cancer but this one is more deadly and dangerous I’m just 37 years old with a 13 year old daughter my cancer is in my lungs, bones, and liver my 13 yr old daughter and I recently didn’t have any where to stay my grandmother out the kindness of her heart who doesn’t have much either offered us a place to stay we are so happy and we are together she’s allowing me to live here while I fight this terminal illness my 82 year old  grandmother literally saved my daughter and my life  I thank God for her I don’t have any money as u can imagine I’m on unemployment and my medication is sky high she refuses to take literally one dime from me she wants me to get better and spend my money on me and my daughter so we can enjoy our time together. Not to mention she has her own illnesses on her own we im a single parent my grandmother is a widow living on social security a nice  I ask for myself a nice massage chair for those time my body ache and the morphine isn’t helping. I have a massage mat but it doesn’t help me at last but last  not least my 13 yr old daughter I was so broke I couldn’t afford to get her anything for her birthday 11/11/98 could you please give her a 4th generation iPod touch. if it’s not too much to ask please provide a 250 court filing fee I’m trying to divorce my emotionally and abusive husband Martrice Blankenship I’m not just making this up in the court records he’s was found guilty I don’t want to die married to a man like him  again my name is Shamunda Phillips 713909-6638 email zon.phillips@yahoo.com thank you for your time.\r\n   ',0,'2011-11-23 20:54:36','2011-11-23 20:54:36'),(13,8,' \r\n\r\n		\r\nMy dear friends in Christ,\r\n\r\n            Greetings in Jesus name. He alone is our Savior and coming King.\r\n Please send us some information about your ministry.  We would be interested in the                                                                                  invitation of the HDQ and a statement about your doctrine. We have focused on helping the scourged people of Haiti and especially the children who are without parents or families and are totally at risk during these difficult days.\r\n    \r\n        I would like for you to come aboard with us in our labor of love for the orphans.  Partner with us to help support these dear orphans of Haiti.  We are ministering to these at risk children trying to give them hope.  They need to know that there are people praising the same God that have come to trust for their very lives. \r\n    \r\n            I have heard that you too love the LORD God.  That is the main reason we are contacting your ministry. Please check out our website at www.cclafo.org.  Notice the photos of the children and the destroyed buildings.  We are rebuilding to protect the children and to minister to them.  We are educating these little ones and trying to get them medical attention. Our website will give you a little more information of this special ministry.  \r\n    \r\nPlease partner with us to rebuild Haiti piece by piece.  Starting with these beautiful and needy children, together we will triumph in the name of the LORD Jesus Christ.  \r\nContact with me, the actual owner, founder and director.  Give me a call at (954) 245-9232.\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n           In the love of our LORD,\r\n                         Rev. Pastor Esaie Prophete \r\n',0,'2011-11-24 22:11:34','2011-11-24 22:11:34'),(14,9,'Hello CAM friends!\r\nTwo months ago I moved to Alabama from Lancaster County, PA to begin a 2 year term of service with We Care Program, a prison ministry. I serve as a chaplain in a women\'s institution.\r\n\r\nThis was the first in several years that I missed the open house.  I do receive your newsletter here at my new address. Could you please mail me a 2012 CAM calender?  I would greatly appreciate it.\r\n\r\nThank you so much,\r\nSharon',0,'2011-11-25 23:56:11','2011-11-25 23:56:11'),(15,10,'Please delete this address. We are no longer at this address. Thanks',0,'2011-11-26 03:26:16','2011-11-26 03:26:16'),(16,11,'Dear Christian Aid Staff,\r\n\r\n Greeting in Jesus\' name! I was wondering about the Sponor-an-Orphan program, if the sponor has any choice in which (country)or orphanage they would support?  \r\n\r\n           Thank you, Missie',0,'2011-11-26 15:10:26','2011-11-26 15:10:26'),(17,12,'I am needed to have information such as catalogs sent to me for our entire family to make donations this year..at our family Christmas we plan to sit down with your catalogs to go over where and what we would like to give to the needy...if at all possible i would need like 6 catalogs..one per family sent so we can each have one to review and make our decisions.  Thank You ever so kindly.\r\nDarcy',0,'2011-11-26 17:01:06','2011-11-26 17:01:06'),(18,13,'Je suis Enel EXUME Responsable d\'une jeune Eglise protestante en Haiti et VKEA la raison pour laquelle je vous ecris c\'est pour vous demander votre aide dans le but de  maider mes moyent sont très faible alors je ne pas les moyents de payer une ecole en Haiti alors je vous ecris pour vous demander votre aide.\r\nsi vous le pouvez envoyer pour nous des chaises et Materielles instrumentale et de la nourriture pour notre Assemblé nous vous enverrons une photos dès les arrivé pour travail du Seigneur,pour que vous voyer mon Ministère \r\nvoici mon adresse: Fr. Enel EXUME 214 rue Macajoux Port-au-prince,Haiti\r\nQue Dieu benisse votre travail\r\n',0,'2011-11-27 03:04:16','2011-11-27 03:04:16'),(19,14,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-11-27 22:46:11','2011-11-27 22:46:11'),(20,15,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-11-28 12:36:46','2011-11-28 12:36:46'),(21,16,'Hello I am trying to reach David Troyer and seek 2 or 3 minutes time on his calendar...I just called and was advised that there was no interest...so I obviously was interpreted as a solicitor, I work for Salem Web in the capacitty of a consultant for potential donor development...I would appreciate the courtesy of a reply for this request in any case.\r\n\r\nThank you and God\'s blessings!\r\n\r\nCurt Baxter',0,'2011-11-28 17:47:53','2011-11-28 17:47:53'),(22,4,'please contact me now!',0,'2011-11-28 19:11:21','2011-11-28 19:11:21'),(23,17,'Dear sir/madam \r\nwe are doing social service for beggars people now 16 children are going to school \r\n 19 small children are  going to day care center we like to give them  new dress for the Christmas we are taking care of there  parents also  they are 12 families we like to show the love of Jesus  in this Christmas  time so we need help to help them  if you are available you can also come and celibate  the Christmas with them\r\n our cell no 0091-9940530036 \r\n\r\n     http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.103008553129862.3641.100002621528155&type=3\r\n\r\n thank you very much\r\nxavier\r\n',0,'2011-11-29 04:45:25','2011-11-29 04:45:25'),(24,18,'Hi would like to find out more information to involve in Christian Aid Ministries program and centers ?  \r\nAs partner a new add on project with the existing program and centers the add on along with activity and resource \r\n material for others to expand and help with the outreach . Came across and \r\nthought the project will fit with the Christian Ministries Organization and as well help in many ways .Will be\r\nglad to send more details of the involvement . Looking forward to hear soon .\r\n \r\nGod Bless & Thanks,\r\n \r\nMaleika Matthews\r\nAM2725@AOL.COM',0,'2011-11-30 07:18:05','2011-11-30 07:18:05'),(25,19,'I am a missionary involved with Baptist Medical and Dental Missions International and I am in need of some Haitian Creole Bibles.  Can I purchase them through you and if so how can I go about doing so.  ',0,'2011-12-02 04:08:25','2011-12-02 04:08:25'),(26,20,'hello my name is ioan and a representative  from your ministry visited my church and told me about all the work that christian aid ministry does in Romania and then i heard about the Nathaniel christian orphanage in Suceauva and i was wondering if there was any volunteer programs or any way for me to volunteer and perhaps help out. I was born in Romania and can speak partial Romanian, i am not 100% fluent but i can read and write a little also. i would love to be able to volunteer so please get back to me on how and if i could actually be able too, thank you and god bless..  ',0,'2011-12-02 04:27:08','2011-12-02 04:27:08'),(27,21,'BACKGROUND: \r\nFoundation for Needy Children Initiative (FONCI) is a community based Development Initiative formed by the Christian Community Members of Northern Division in Mbale Municipality. The Foundation was established to respond to children and community needs using a holistic approach of the Millennium age in social, economic and spiritual aspects of life i.e. Education, HIV/AIDS, malaria other related to community needs. The Foundation is registered with NGO Board Kampala, Ministry of Internal affairs (Reg. No) S.5914/8101. \r\n\r\n Due to the insufficient help and work in partnership we have therefore do request you to support/ help our organization. \r\n\r\nWe shall be grateful if our request is put under your positive consideration. \r\n\r\nWe wait to hear from you. \r\n\r\nThanks, \r\n\r\n',0,'2011-12-02 15:34:42','2011-12-02 15:34:42'),(28,22,'We are interested in getting copies of the 101 favorite stories from the Bible and 25 favorite stories from the Bible in english.  our church is involved in a mission in Haiti.  We would like to look at the books in english before we send them there.  Can you tell me what i need to do.\r\nBlessings,\r\njeff Walker',0,'2011-12-02 16:31:44','2011-12-02 16:31:44'),(29,23,'If it is convenient please send a copy of the open house CD-ROM set to us here. Thank you and may God continue to bless your wonderful ministry.',0,'2011-12-02 19:52:55','2011-12-02 19:52:55'),(30,24,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-12-02 20:54:57','2011-12-02 20:54:57'),(31,25,'I would like to mail a check for a money donation to the Sponsor-an-Orphan fund. Where can I mail my check to and can I designate on the check that I want the money to go to sponsor-an-orphan?\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\nChristine',0,'2011-12-03 19:22:09','2011-12-03 19:22:09'),(32,26,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-12-05 04:41:22','2011-12-05 04:41:22'),(33,27,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2011-12-05 14:42:06','2011-12-05 14:42:06'),(34,5,'This is a production level test of new type for email.\r\n',0,'2011-12-05 17:23:15','2011-12-05 17:23:15'),(35,28,'this is a