r received some medicines and such from your organization last year, and I was wondering if you could help us get some vitamins for our kids here at our Day Center. We need around 100 packets of multivitamins every 3 months. Can you help us find some? We would be happy to help with shipping or anything! We wanted to order them from the USA but the company said they would not send to Romania. Thank you for your kind consideration, May God richly bless you in Return.\r\n\r\nSincerely, Tresha M. McKnight',0,'2012-02-29 13:54:00','2012-02-29 13:54:00'),(296,273,'La Charité supérieure à tout autre don\r\nEn lisant le passage biblique dans 1 Corinthiens 13.2-3, j\'ai été frappé par son contenu qui dit : \"Et quand j\'aurais le don de prophétie, la science de tous les mystères et toute la connaissance, quand j\'aurais même toute la foi juqu\'à transporter des montagnes, si je n\'ai pas la charité, je ne suis rien. Et quand je distribuerais tous mes biens pour la nourriture des pauvres, quand je livrerais même mon corps pour être brûlé, si je n\'ai pas la charité, cela ne me sert de rien\".\r\n \r\nConnaissant votre façon de travailler, le souci et le zèle qui animent pour apporter concours aux étudiants africains, nous tenons à vous informer que la bibliothèque de notre école se trouve dans une situation dépassant tout entendement, triste et déplorable.\r\n \r\nC\'est ainsi nous vous exhortons d\'avoir un coeur pour ces étudiants qui manquent un peu de tout c\'est-à-dire les Bibles et les livres pour leur édification , leur recherche et leur formation, eu égard de ce qui précède, la solution ne viendra que de Dieu par l\'entremise de votre part dont le ministère vous est confié.\r\n \r\nPour clore, nous avons pour cette année 147 étudiants.\r\n \r\nNous continuons à prier pour votre ministère, pour vous et tout le personnel qui vous entoure. Nous comptons sur votre tendresse, bonne volonté pour débloquer cette situation combien triste et lamentable que nos étudiants sont entrain de vivre. Toutefois, nous sommes dans l\'attente de votre réponse. \r\n \r\nVotre frère Evoloko Kumbi\r\nInstitut Biblique de Kitomesa\r\nBP 388 Kinshasa 20\r\nKinshasa 20\r\nRépublique Démocratique du Congo',0,'2012-02-29 16:22:29','2012-02-29 16:22:29'),(297,274,'I have been asked to supply the names of any transportation companies who serve Port au Prince , Haiti. We had shipments come in via CAM and TGS. Are you all that company?',0,'2012-02-29 21:27:50','2012-02-29 21:27:50'),(298,275,'To Whom It May Concern:\r\nI am experiencing great financial difficulty at this time in my life. I just lost my job and have applied for food stamps and unemployment benefits, but have not recieved the benefits yet. I do not start my new job until next week and have no income coming into my house right now. I am frantically seeking emergency cash assistance to help me pay my rent of $425 due this Friday March 2, 2012. I have no family to help and my friends are unable to help me in this difficult time. I have contacted two chairities and organizations in my area who are not able to help at this time. I have been praying that God will bring me through this difficult time. I am seeking help. If your charity can help in any way possible, please contact me. 740-543-8888 or 740-457-2961. Thank you and Sincerely, Diane Wilhelm',0,'2012-02-29 21:56:29','2012-02-29 21:56:29'),(299,276,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-01 15:25:05','2012-03-01 15:25:05'),(300,277,'We would like to send a donation to a Christian charity that works to help the poor people in Romania that do not have enought money to provide for food, shelter and clothing!\r\n\r\nBaird Kinney',0,'2012-03-01 15:35:38','2012-03-01 15:35:38'),(301,278,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-01 19:28:25','2012-03-01 19:28:25'),(302,279,' Who do we contact - we have a group interested in helping with clean-up or rebuilding somewhere?',0,'2012-03-01 22:14:41','2012-03-01 22:14:41'),(303,280,'Good afternoon!\r\nThe Christian rehabilitation center in Republic Kazakhstan, the East Kazakhstan area, Ridder opens.\r\nIf you in heart have a desire to help narcodependent, to people with alcoholic dependence we will be glad to any help.\r\nThe help on purchase of the house for the rehabilitation center (5-10 thousand dollars) is required.\r\nAlso we will be glad to any help - materials, books, records, experience, prayful support. If the Lord encloses desire in your heart - write sergridd@inbox.ru.\r\n\r\nWe guarantee that in our desire to serve people in rehabilitation, there is no deceit and a personal interest, undertake to give the full report on an expenditure of means, to give any necessary documents.\r\n\r\nIf you know Christian service who is engaged in service of rehabilitation and can help, send please to them this letter.\r\n\r\n38 Give, and it shall be given unto you; good measure, pressed down, and shaken together, and running over, shall men give into your bosom. For with the same measure that ye mete withal it shall be measured to you again.\r\n(Lk.6:38)\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Lord bless you!\r\nYours faithfully, yours in the Christ, Grachev Sergey.\r\n',0,'2012-03-02 12:47:25','2012-03-02 12:47:25'),(304,281,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-03-02 16:51:34','2012-03-02 16:51:34'),(305,282,'Be loved Greetings in Jesus name.I am a pastor Reinhard from India I am doing ministry in un reached villages and tribal hills  in south and North India.through Gospel healing crusades more than 120 churches were planted.we started day school for  more than 155 tribal children.please pray for this ministries.We want to work with underChristian Aid Ministries.kindly send your valuable reply.thanking you,\r\nYours In His Mission,\r\nReinhard   ',0,'2012-03-02 18:44:30','2012-03-02 18:44:30'),(306,283,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-02 20:15:11','2012-03-02 20:15:11'),(307,284,'MA NUMESC CANELA ONISIM DOMICILIAT COMUN NICULESTI,JUDETUL DAMBOVITA,SAT CIOCANA