nd robbery people live. \r\nThe people living in this area are below the poverty line without even having a single square meal a day. Many die an early death due to alcohol, sickness and due to hazardous job they have to take. The people living in this area are uneducated and very poor people.\r\n    From 1981, I serve God with my wife Mary Babu who is a trained teacher especially for mentally handicapped children. She gave her hand in Rock Church Ministry. In the same year God blessed us with a female baby named Beaulah Mercy Mary. \r\n     By thanking Him she also dedicated her for His vineyard now she is a nursing college lecturer serving God among youth and sick people in hospital along with her husband named Mr. Ajay Kumar who serve God among lay people working in companies and colleges in Hyderabad and Bangalore city. He knows more than 5 Indian languages which help him to easily communicate with people \r\n Sir, Please pray for us, because our church faces lot of persecution for example that the Hindu religion comprising Hindu Munnani, R.S.S and Hindu Forward Block and Hindu Parished against our church activities\r\nPastor !We  Welcoming you and your Team to Visit us at our  Kanmalai Church( Rock Church) , Chennai-12 to share love and fellowship and Gods Words. Our church door and our hearts are always open. Our church is located in a rural place. It is five kilometers away from the Chennai Central Railway station. And it is quite opposite to Jeeva Railway station and 15 kilometers from Meenampakam International Airport. To directly see us and our church people.    .\r\n  Pastor!  Kindly keep our ministries in your prayer and stretch your helping hand for our ministry and for our church people .We will gladly accept offerings and any donations.\r\n      We are praying for you and your ministry. God Bless You Richly\r\nThank you very much,                                                                   Have a good day\r\n  Photo of Ps M. Theodore Williams Babu\r\n                                 Church .Add; Kanmalai, #27, Dr.Ambedkar College Rd, Chennai-600012\r\nYours in His Service, In the love of the Father.  \r\n Ps .M.T.W.BABU\r\nfounder of  Kanmalai Church.      Res Add: #19,2nd Main Road,\r\n                                           K.K.R Garden  Thapalpetti, Madhavaram, Chennai-600060.\r\n                                        Mobile No; 9840665338, 9840413929,E-mail:  mtwbabu@gmail.com\r\n',0,'2012-03-12 05:25:54','2012-03-12 05:25:54'),(344,320,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-12 18:42:41','2012-03-12 18:42:41'),(345,321,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-03-12 21:24:42','2012-03-12 21:24:42'),(346,322,'I was wondering if I could get some information on mission trips that might be taking place this summer?',0,'2012-03-12 22:25:09','2012-03-12 22:25:09'),(347,323,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-03-13 06:40:07','2012-03-13 06:40:07'),(348,325,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-03-14 00:11:09','2012-03-14 00:11:09'),(349,326,'Good morning,\r\n\r\nMy name is Olga Aleksandrova, I’m from Kiew, Ukraine.\r\n\r\nI’ve been accepted by 12 universities in London for LLM course 2012/13. Unfortunately,\r\nI’m not capable to pay for my studying at the University because I have no money savings \r\nconsidering that I’ve graduated from Ukrainian university only half a year ago.\r\n\r\nTaking into account my difficult financial situation, I’m looking for sponsorship/grant to\r\ncover the tuition fees and living costs at one of these universities.\r\n\r\nI had been working in position of junior associate in the law firm\r\nand my salary was minimal, in other words, it corresponded to the occupied\r\nposition at that moment. I don’t have other incomings and financial support\r\ninsomuch as I live with my mum – retiree only. \r\n\r\nMy study at bachelor’s program of the National Taras Shevchenko University of\r\nKyiv was sponsored by my mother due to the fact that she was employed at