t I know that I should do to be a good husband and to be a good Evangelist how to preach the word of God for people to receive Christ and how to get people healed. My wife and I started having problems and they got bigger and bigger and then it got in to the ministry. It got to be to much for us and I decided I was going to find some where else to live. Then I meet a lady that helped me to for get all my problems and that produced a son. My wife and I had no children and she did not want any. She wanted only me in her house. It came down to my only son or my wife and the ministry. I chose my son! I lost ever thing. My wife my ministry and all my friends for what I had done. I even gave up on God because I thought I had done the worse thing that I could do to Him and the Church by getting in sin. 3 years latter we also had a daughter. Through the love that I have found for my children I now know how to love my father God with all my heart, soul and strength. I now have a true relationship from my heart not my head. I am now closer to my father God than I have ever been in my life. My deepest desire is to fix my problems and go back to doing what God has called me to do. Last year I got before God and cried out unto Him. I wanted all my problems fixed and back in to the Ministry. I began fasten and prayer. God told me to write letters to apologise for what I had done. As time went on I got closer to God that I have ever been. I had stayed with the mother of my children through thick and thin just to be with the children. To make sure nothing would happen to them. Last month God told me that I had to get out of the relationship that I was in with her because of sin. I have stayed with her to pray for her. Standing in faith that God would change her life. Of course that was up to her. A pastor gave me the chance to move in to a church in another City. God started moving  stronger in me the day I moved. After 3 weeks I moved in to a apartment that was give rent free and 