id. While the Dept. of Education does have a rehabilitation program that would allow me to return these loans into good standing after 12 months, the program requires that timely payments be made for at least 6 months before I can once again become eligible for federal grants and/or loans. This creates a difficult situation for me as I was greatly looking forward to graduating with my Bachelor\'s degree in the fall of this year. I am also a divorced mother of 6 yr. old twins of whom I am trying very hard to regain custody and would love to be able to show the courts that I have achieved this major accomplishment. I have struggled over the past six months or so with the loss of my children, my recent divorce, an eviction from my home, and my father unexpectedly passing away in March. I have been working very hard since entering treatment in April to focus on my recovery and begin to put the pieces of my life back together, and would love nothing more than to take this next step by completing my education, however my financial situation just will not allow me to afford the cost of tuition without some assistance. I have been looking for work since I have been here in town, and have checked into scholarships offered by Radford University, but at the moment I am still unemployed and unfortunately scholarship money has been exhausted by this point in the school year. Please let me know if there is an opportunity that I may be unaware of, and I will gladly do my part to do anything I can to help in any way. My phone number is 804-221-8367<tel:804-221-8367>. Thank you for your consideration. Sincerely, Allison',0,'2012-06-22 16:27:13','2012-06-22 16:27:13'),(673,618,'Good afternoon,  \r\n\r\nMy husband owns a dental practice in Lancaster County and we are looking to donate our used Panoramic X-ray machine.  I didn\'t know if that was something your organization would be interested in utilizing but I thought I\'d reach out to you to see if it was a possibility.  If so, I can certainly forward photographs and more details.  We also have a film processor that we are willing to donate along with the x-ray machine. \r\n\r\nThank you for your time, \r\nJennifer Lenahan \r\n717-468-2545\r\nlenahans@comcast.net ',0,'2012-06-22 20:25:44','2012-06-22 20:25:44'),(674,619,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-06-24 05:50:04','2012-06-24 05:50:04'),(675,620,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-06-24 14:31:29','2012-06-24 14:31:29'),(676,621,'Newsletter Signup Form Submittal',0,'2012-06-24 22:47:57','2012-06-24 22:47:57'),(677,622,'I would like to please contact Concard Swetzertruber. I visited your ministries headquarter in Phelediapha in noverber of 1998 when I first arrie in america. pls call me also on 423-371-8991.',0,'2012-06-25 14:33:38','2012-06-25 14:33:38'),(678,623,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-06-25 22:18:46','2012-06-25 22:18:46'),(679,624,'Hi,\r\nCould you please cancel the 2011 Annual Report that you send to my Windsor address.  I would like to just sign up online.  If you have an e-newsletter that would be great to get that.\r\nThanks, Katherine.',0,'2012-06-26 04:02:08','2012-06-26 04:02:08'),(680,625,'Hello Dear beloved Loving Pastor and family in Lord Jesus Christ, \r\n \r\nGreetings in the name of Jesus Christ. Here When I was browsing on internet I found your name by the spirit of God moved upon me. I believe that here It is not accident that I visits your website, but it is Gods will and His plan for both of us to do His great ministry together in one faith. Amen Thank you for your website. I am wondered and well appreciate you, your family and I agreed with your faith and love.\r\n\r\nMy name Sunil Paul Chapala from India. I have been doing His great Ministry and social service from several years in our areas with independently through the inspired of Jesus word that love each other as Jesus have loves you. John 15; 12. So, I am connecting you for the encouragements in the lord. I need your spiritual directions and prayerful supports for increase our blessed ministry in India. So I would like to join with you, your fellowship for work together in one faith and one love.\r\n\r\nI request you that if there is any possible to you there. Please come to India and encourage our churches with your truths and charity. I believe that many unreached people can reach to kingdom of God through your Visiting of India. You are always to visit my churches and ministry at any time. I will arrange gospel meetings, pastors Conferences, church visits for you in India. Please be kind upon India and teach me with your wonderful truths and faith. We will be praying for you and your family and your jobs. Please pray for me, my family and ministry efforts of orphans, widows, leprous and pastors and all of our ministry.\r\n\r\nOur Ministry Prayers Requests;\r\n\r\n1. Need Food for Orphans, Widows, Leprous, ect!\r\n2. Need Salaries for 20 Pastors to do His Ministry\r\n3. Need Church Construction Cost for worship God\r\n4. Need 20 Bicycles & a Van for Our gospel Itinerary\r\n5. Need Electrical Sound Systems for Meetings\r\n6. Need 500 Telugu Bible for Distribute freely\r\n7. Need Gospel Tracts Prints Cost and Medical Camps\r\n\r\nThank you for your prayers, please convey my hearty thanks to your family, friends, and churches. We pray that the Lord will touch your loving heart for connections and partnerships with us that will help us advance our ministry. \r\n\r\nThank you so much. I am looking forward to hear from you the word.\r\n \r\nSincerely in Christ Love\r\n \r\nPastor. Sunil Paul Chapala\r\nPhone; 011-91-8855278644\r\n\r\nVisit our website; http://www.loveeachotherministries.org\r\n\r\n\r\nMy Postal Mail Address\r\n \r\nPastor. Sunil Paul Chapala\r\nLove Each Other Ministries\r\nJonnada (P.O.BOX) 533233\r\n(Via) Alamuru, E.G. Distract\r\nAndhra Pradesh, South India\r\n',0,'2012-06-26 04:14:35','2012-06-26 04:14:35'),(681,626,'I would be interested in a short-term mission. (3-6