ird world day-to-day and need a \"hand up\". The way I see it, if I can be an advocate for Missert, why can\'t he be one of the folks that gets some help. \r\n\r\nI Would love to talk to someone in your organization about what if anything can be done here.\r\n\r\nSincerely,\r\nMario Pecchia\r\nmario.pecchia@cmc.com\r\n205-362-7364',0,'2012-07-17 15:44:28','2012-07-17 15:44:28'),(752,692,'Newsletter Signup From New Account',0,'2012-07-17 22:28:11','2012-07-17 22:28:11'),(753,693,'We, do have a foster home that has been sponsor by individual but this time they can not continue to support the homes due to their family low income so the homes is facing problems in the following areas such as;\r\n1 food ,formula food(milk),medication for the kids, caregiver salaries, rent for caregivers and kids, and stipend for staff. \r\nPresently the home has 13 kids with special needs that was abounded in the hospital and in the community and some have no family members and their hope of survivor is base on the organization along with 5kids that was brought to our homes by their relatives so, we could be grateful if you will come to our call to make these kids feel that God love them. I am the country Director for this organization and my contact number is 23188379904 .we will be happy if we are call for an inquiry.\r\nThanks for your concerned .\r\nDaniel Mulbah.       ',0,'2012-07-18 11:32:00','2012-07-18 11:32:00'),(754,694,'\r\n\r\n\r\nanglais\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nfrançais\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\narabe\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nT & G Professional School salute you and congratulate you for the work you do within the Haitian community. T & G a professional working in the school acadrement disadvantaged youth, Take the opportunity to ask for your help in us helping in this hard work. We need chairs, computers, equipment for construction.Because that these young people lack the means.\r\n Waiting for your reply, I beg you to accept or Ms. M\'s expresion of my highest consideration.',0,'2012-07